""
"""  Keymaps :)
""""

"" Near esc key
imap jk      <Esc>
vmap jk      <Esc>


"" Disable arrow keys
map  <Left>  <Nop>
map  <Right> <Nop>
map  <Up>    <Nop>
map  <Down>  <Nop>

imap <Left>  <Nop>
imap <Right> <Nop>
imap <Up>    <Nop>
imap <Down>  <Nop>


"" Save file
map  <C-S>   <Cmd>w<CR>
map! <C-S>   <Cmd>w<CR>


"" Quit without save
map  <C-Q>   <Cmd>q<CR>
map! <C-Q>   <Cmd>q<CR>

